            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "Effortless Old-World courtliness over Californian informality; never raises his voice. Voice fingerprint: (1) graceful European formality bleeding into West-Coast ease, (2) patronage framed as generosity, (3) a predator's patience. Sample lines: \"Such potential, cara. You should sit for Eidolon, the light here is forgiving.\" / \"Your grandfather and I disagree on nearly everything. Almost a shame.\" Crack: when his courtly mask slips under real challenge, the ancient predator shows for a breath before he recovers.",
